name: amgm_new_p1
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p1 (x y z: ℝ) (hx : x > 0) (hy : y > 0) (hz : z > 0) : (x + y) / 2 ≥ (x * y) ^ (2⁻¹: ℝ ) := by

name: amgm_new_p2
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p2 (x y: ℝ) (hx : x > 0) (hy : y > 0) : (x + 2 * y) / 3 ≥ (x * y * y) ^ (3⁻¹: ℝ ) := by

name: amgm_new_p3
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p3 (x y z w: ℝ) (hx : x > 0) (hy : y > 0) (hz : z > 0) (hw : w > 0) : (x + y + z + z) / 5 ≥ (x * y * z * z) ^ (4⁻¹: ℝ ) := by

name: amgm_new_p8
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p8 (x y z: ℝ ) (h₁: x+ y + z = 6) (h₂ : x > 0 ∧ y> 0 ∧ z> 0): (x * y * z) ^ (3⁻¹: ℝ ) ≤ 2 := by

name: amgm_new_p9
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p9 (x y: ℝ ) (h₁: 2 * x+ y = 3) (h₂ : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): (x ^ 2 * y) ^ (3⁻¹: ℝ ) ≤ 1 := by

name: amgm_new_p10
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p10 (x y: ℝ ) (h₁: 2 * x+ y = 3) (h₂ : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): x ^ 2 * y ≤ 1 := by

name: amgm_new_p11
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p11 (x y z: ℝ ) (h₁: x+ y + z = 6) (h₂ : x > 0 ∧ y> 0 ∧ z> 0): x * y * z ≤ 8 := by

name: amgm_new_p12
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p12 (x y z: ℝ ) (h₁: 2 * x+ 2 * y + z = 10) (h₂ : x > 0 ∧ y> 0 ∧ z> 0): x^2 * y ^ 2 * z ≤ 32 := by

name: amgm_new_p13
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p13 (x y: ℝ )  (h : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): (3:ℝ) / 5 * x ^ 5 + (2:ℝ) / 5 * y ^ 5  ≥ x^3 * y^2 := by

name: amgm_new_p14
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p14 (x y: ℝ )  (h : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): (2:ℝ) / 3 * y ^ 6 + (1:ℝ) / 3 * x ^ 6  ≥ y^4 * x^2 := by

name: amgm_new_p15
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p15 (x y: ℝ )  (h : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): (5:ℝ) / 7 * x ^ 7 + (2:ℝ) / 7 * y ^ 7  ≥ x^5 * y^2 := by

name: amgm_new_p16
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p16 (x y: ℝ )  (h : x > 0 ∧ y> 0): (2:ℝ) / 3 * y ^ 3 + (1:ℝ) / 3 * x ^ 3  ≥ y^2 * x := by

name: amgm_new_p24
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p24 (a b c : ℝ) (ap : a > 0) (bp : b> 0) (cp : c> 0) (g : a * b * c = 1) : a^3 + b^3 + c^3 ≥ a / c + b / a + c / b := by

name: amgm_new_p25
formal_statement: theorem amgm_new_p25 (a b c : ℝ) (ap : a > 0) (bp : b> 0) (cp : c> 0) : a^7 + b^7 + c^7 ≥ a^5 * b^2 + b^5 * c^2 + c^5 * a^2 := by
